'''Michael Fellman''' (1943, [[Lincoln, Nebraska]] – 2012 [[Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]])  Professor Emeritus of History at 
[[Simon Fraser University]] in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sfu.ca/history/faculty-and-staff/retired/michael-fellman.html|title=Fellman, Michael - Department of History - Simon Fraser University|publisher=}}</ref>  Fellman was educated at the [[University of Michigan]] (BA, 1965) and [[Northwestern University]] (PhD, 1969). He was the son of [[David Fellman]], Vilas Professor Emeritus at the [[University of Wisconsin, Madison]].

