'''''The Might That Was Assyria''''' (1984; {{ISBN|0-283-98961-0}}) is written by [[Assyriology|Assyriologist]] [[H. W. F. Saggs]]. It illustrates the [[Neo-Assyrian Empire]]. Saggs spent half of his life studying the ancient Assyrians, before he wrote this book.

